e that captures fast-moving subjects and doesn’t let go. The liberating ɑ7 II. Packed with innovation yet compact beyond compare, it frees you to shoot however you like with confidence. \n*1 Among interchangeable-lens digital cameras equipped with a 35mm full-frame image sensor. As of November 2014 based on Sony research.","styleRuns":[{"startIndex":0,"length":841,"styleRunExtensions":{"styleRunColorMapExtension":{"colorMap":[{"key":"USER_INTERFACE_THEME_DARK","value":4294967295},{"key":"USER_INTERFACE_THEME_LIGHT","value":4279440147}]}},"fontFamilyName":"Roboto"}]},"headerRuns":[{"startIndex":0,"length":841,"headerMapping":"ATTRIBUTED_STRING_HEADER_MAPPING_UNSPECIFIED"}],"backgroundColorStyle":"BACKGROUND_COLOR_STYLE_COLOR_SAMPLED","lightThemeColorPalette":{"baseBackground":4294963952,"raisedBackground":4294963952,"additiveBackground":566842949,"textPrimary":4281928966,"textSecondary":4286853156,"invertedBackground":4287571993,"overlayBackground":3426290950},"darkThemeColorPalette":{"baseBackground":4280091906,"raisedBackground":4281928966,"additiveBackground":734615109,"textPrimary":4294763230,"textSecondary":4293568671,"invertedBackground":4293101949,"overlayBackground":3426290950},"colorSampledDescriptionBodyText":{"content":"Full-frame, palm-sized α. Perfection for all. Stability for all.\nBreathtaking image quality meets unrivaled shooting freedom in the ɑ7 II, the world’s first*1 full-frame camera with 5-axis image stabilization. Now you can fully express your vision with full-frame quality and cutting-edge camera shake compensation compatible with wide-ranging lenses. But Sony didn’t stop there. Operation is incredibly intuitive and enhanced Fast Hybrid AF delivers lightning-fast focusing, super-wide coverage and tracking performance that captures fast-moving subjects and doesn’t let go. The liberating ɑ7 II. Packed with innovation yet compact beyond compare, it frees you to shoot however you like with confidence. \n*1 Among interchangeable-lens digital came